trans-unit.source: Provides a set of ASP.NET run-time services for the current application.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder et sett med tjenester for ASP.NET-kjøretid for dette programmet.

trans-unit.source: The HttpRuntime object is used at the beginning of the ASP.NET pipeline model that processes HTTP requests.
trans-unit.target: HttpRuntime-objektet brukes på begynnelsen av ASP.NET pipeline modellen som behandler HTTP-forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpRuntime.ProcessRequest%2A> method drives all subsequent ASP.NET Web processing.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.HttpRuntime.ProcessRequest%2A>metoden styrer alle etterfølgende ASP.NET Web behandling.</xref:System.Web.HttpRuntime.ProcessRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: Page developers can use the HttpRuntime class properties to find out information about the current application domain for diagnostic purposes, for example.
trans-unit.target: Siden utviklere kan bruke klasseegenskaper HttpRuntime til å få informasjon om gjeldende programdomenet for diagnoseformål, for eksempel.

trans-unit.source: Developers creating custom process pipeline or a custom hosting environment should call the <xref:System.Web.HttpRuntime.ProcessRequest%2A> method from a class derived from the <xref:System.Web.HttpWorkerRequest> or <xref:System.Web.Hosting.SimpleWorkerRequest> class.
trans-unit.target: Utviklere å opprette egendefinerte prosessen pipeline eller en egendefinert vertsmiljøet må kalle <xref:System.Web.HttpRuntime.ProcessRequest%2A>metoden fra en klasse som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.HttpWorkerRequest>eller <xref:System.Web.Hosting.SimpleWorkerRequest>klasse.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.SimpleWorkerRequest> </xref:System.Web.HttpWorkerRequest> </xref:System.Web.HttpRuntime.ProcessRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: The application restarts the next time a request is received for it.
trans-unit.target: Programmet starter på nytt neste gang en forespørsel er mottatt for den.

trans-unit.source: `UnloadAppDomain` is useful for servers that have a large number of applications that infrequently receive requests.
trans-unit.target: `UnloadAppDomain`er nyttig for servere som har et stort antall programmer som mottar sjelden forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: Rather than keep application resources alive for the lifetime of the process, `UnloadAppDomain` allows programmatic shutdown of unused applications.
trans-unit.target: I stedet for å beholde programmet ressurser aktiv for levetiden for prosessen `UnloadAppDomain` tillater programmatisk avslutning av programmer.
